snippet.title: First Pic of Tekashi 6ix9ine in Jail Emerges | News 4 Now
snippet.description:
Rapper Tekashi 6ix9ine -- also known as Tekashi69, Tekashi 69, and 6ix9ine --was photographed for the first time in jail on Tuesday, as he grabbed his girlfriend Jade’s butt on an image posted to her Instagram. 

The rapper, is in federal custody on racketeering and firearms charges for his alleged involvement with a violent New York City gang, the Nine Trey Gangstas. 

Anchor Stefan Holt also reports on a plan to give all New Yorkers access to health care, a shooting at a Macy’s in Brooklyn and a special delivery in a New York City taxi.
